name: AeroShell Fluid 4 (NA)

packs.name: Can 1 US Gal T/H Tinplate Pre-printed (6)

marketing: AeroShell Fluid 4  (NA) is a mineral hydraulic oil with very good low temperature characteristics and capable of operating over a wide temperature range. AeroShell Fluid 4  (NA) is composed of a mineral oil base stock and a complex additive package which results in a product with excellent low temperature flow and anti-wear properties, exceptional antifoam characteristics, and excellent oxidation stability. AeroShell Fluid 4 (NA) is dyed red.
